"title": "5345: influence",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5345",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The ability to affect others or events. Also, the experience of being affected by someone or something else. Scripture recognises the wide-ranging power of influence for both good and evil.</p>\n<h2>Teaching on influence</h2>\n<h3>Exhortations to be influenced by good and to influence others for good</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:13-Matt5:16\">MAT 5:13–5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:8-Prov1:9\">PRO 1:8–1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:1-Prov7:5\">PRO 7:1–7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:15\">PRO 25:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:8-Phil4:9\">PHP 4:8–4:9</a></p>\n<h3>Exhortations to resist evil influence and not to be a bad influence</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:15-Deut4:19\">DEU 4:15–4:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:1-Prov5:14\">PRO 5:1–5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:20-Prov6:26\">PRO 6:20–6:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:5-Matt18:6\">MAT 18:5–18:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:13\">ROM 14:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:6-1Cor5:8\">1CO 5:6–5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:9-1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:9–8:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:14-2Cor6:18\">2CO 6:14–6:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:14\">2TI 2:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7\">JAS 4:7</a></p>\n<h2>Good influence in its various contexts</h2>\n<h3>The influence of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:1-Acts2:13\">ACT 2:1–2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26-Acts8:40\">ACT 8:26–8:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6-Acts16:10\">ACT 16:6–16:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:17\">ROM 8:5–8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26-Rom8:27\">ROM 8:26–8:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:10-1Cor2:16\">1CO 2:10–2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:3\">1CO 12:3</a></p>\n<h3>People of good influence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:5\">2TI 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:41-Gen41:43\">GEN 41:41–41:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:1-1Kgs10:9\">1KI 10:1–10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:11-1Kgs15:14\">1KI 15:11–15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:1-2Kgs18:8\">2KI 18:1–18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:1-2Kgs23:25\">2KI 23:1–23:25</a></p>\n<h2>Evil influence in its various contexts</h2>\n<h3>People of evil influence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:22\">2KI 9:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:1-Matt15:14\">MAT 15:1–15:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:5-Matt16:12\">MAT 16:5–16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:13-Matt23:15\">MAT 23:13–23:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:20\">MAT 27:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3-2Cor11:4\">2CO 11:3–11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:13-2Cor11:15\">2CO 11:13–11:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1-2Pet2:3\">2PE 2:1–2:3</a></p>\n<h3>Corrupting influence of evil cultures</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:6-Josh23:8\">JOS 23:6–23:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:12-Josh23:13\">JOS 23:12–23:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:10-Judg2:13\">JDG 2:10–2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:1-1Kgs11:6\">1KI 11:1–11:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:1-Ezra9:2\">EZR 9:1–9:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:15-Neh13:27\">NEH 13:15–13:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:1-1Cor12:2\">1CO 12:1–12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:33\">1CO 15:33</a></p>\n<h3>The influence of Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:23\">MAT 16:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:23-Mark1:26\">MRK 1:23–1:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:33-Luke4:35\">LUK 4:33–4:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:15\">MRK 4:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:19\">MAT 13:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:12\">LUK 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:3-Luke22:4\">LUK 22:3–22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:27-John13:30\">JHN 13:27–13:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7\">2CO 12:7</a></p>\n<h2>Further aspects of influence</h2>\n<h3>The influence of prayer</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:20-Gen18:33\">GEN 18:20–18:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:9-Exod32:14\">EXO 32:9–32:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:13-2Chr7:15\">2CH 7:13–7:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:1-Dan9:23\">DAN 9:1–9:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:3-Jonah3:10\">JON 3:3–3:10</a></p>\n<h3>The influence of words</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:18\">PRO 12:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:4\">PRO 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:23-Prov16:24\">PRO 16:23–16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:23\">PRO 28:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:5-Jas3:6\">JAS 3:5–3:6</a></p>\n<h3>The influence of parents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:8-Prov1:9\">PRO 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr22:2-2Chr22:3\">2CH 22:2–22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:1-Prov4:4\">PRO 4:1–4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:20-Prov6:22\">PRO 6:20–6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:5\">2TI 1:5</a></p>",
